product.title: SVOPES Deck Balusters, 51 Pack, 32.25 in. x 1 in. Iron Metal Spindles, Staircase Railing for Wood & Composite Decks
product.description: 51-Pack Iron Deck Balusters, Durable, Stylish, and Easy to Install, These premium iron balusters are perfect for giving your deck or staircase a sleek, modern update. Crafted from high-quality iron with a black powder-coated finish, they stand up to outdoor elements and maintain their beauty for years. Designed for easy installation, the pre-drilled holes and included screws allow for quick setup, ensuring your deck is both secure and visually appealing. Durable Iron Material, 51-Pack of 32.25 in. Balusters, Sleek Modern Design, Effortless Installation.
feature_bullets: Durable iron construction ensures long-lasting use
Pre-drilled holes and included screws for easy installation
Wave-shaped, contemporary design adds a stylish touch
descriptive_attributes: Easy Installation with Pre-Drilled Holes: Installing these balusters is quick and hassle-free. Each one comes with pre-drilled holes at both ends, allowing for easy attachment to your deck or stair frame. The included 204 self-tapping screws make the process even faster

Durable Iron Construction: Made from high-quality iron, these balusters are resistant to warping, rust, and corrosion, ensuring that your deck railings remain secure and in excellent condition for years. Their sturdy build also enhances the overall safety of your railing system

Modern, Curved Design: With a wave-shaped, contemporary design and a matte black finish, these balusters add a stylish, modern touch to your deck, porch, or stairs. The powder-coated surface is weather-resistant and ensures long-lasting durability in various environmental conditions

51-Piece Set for Large Projects: Each pack contains 51 balusters, each measuring 32.25 in. (82 cm) in length and 1 in. (2.5 cm) in width. This generous quantity is perfect for completing larger railing projects. The size and amount fit most standard deck or stair installations

Versatile for Multiple Settings: These balusters are ideal for a range of applications. Whether for your deck, porch, balcony, stairway, or backyard, they offer an attractive and secure solution. They are compatible with wood and composite deck materials, making them a versatile choice for any project
Specifications: Material: Iron,Baluster Quantity: 51,Screws Quantity: 204,Color: Black,Product Size: 82 x 2.5 cm (32.25 in. x 1 in.)
Package Content: 204 x Screws,51 x Deck Baluster
